Legend:
    [STICK]: Joystick control; push up: forward/up, etc.
    [CLICK]: Runs after clicked once

Gamepad 1:
Drive:
    [STICK] L/R Joysticks: Field Centric with Mecanum

Intake:
    Intake Arm & Slides:
        Base Preset: [CLICK] DPad Down
        Sample Preset: [CLICK] DPad Up
        Transfer Preset: [CLICK] DPad Left
    Intake Slides:
        Fine Control Up: [CLICK] Y
        Fine Control Down: [CLICK] A

    Intake Claw:
        Claw Toggle: [CLICK] Right Bumper


Gamepad 2:
Outtake:
    Outtake Slides:
        Wall Preset: [CLICK] DPad Down
        Chamber Preset: [CLICK] DPad Left
        Score Chamber Preset: [CLICK] DPad Up
        Basket Preset: [CLICK] DPad Right

    Outtake Claw:
        Claw Toggle: [CLICK] Right Bumper

    Ascent:
        [STICK] R Joysticks: Ascent Up/Down

